## Formula E Relevance

RaceCAN Digital Kit is relevant to Formula E low voltage electronics because it models the type of system used to monitor vehicle signals, detect unsafe conditions, and communicate module status across a vehicle network.

The project shows preparation for work involving:

1. Low voltage telemetry
2. Sensor data acquisition
3. CAN bus communication
4. Embedded systems logic
5. Safety oriented fault handling
6. Debugging and documentation
